# Harnessd environment variables
#
# Copy to .env and fill in values. The harness auto-loads .env from
# the harness/ directory on startup. Use --env <path> for a custom path.
#
# Shell environment takes precedence — .env values won't override
# variables already set in your shell.

# ── Research Tools ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Perplexity: enables web-grounded research in planner/builder/evaluator.
# Get a key at https://docs.perplexity.ai/
PERPLEXITY_API_KEY=

# ── Backend Overrides (optional) ───────────────────────────────
# Claude Agent SDK: works without a key if logged into Claude Code
# subscription locally. Set this only to override with a direct API key.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Codex CLI: works without a key if logged into Codex subscription
# locally. Set this only to override with a direct API key.
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
